<subsection xml:id="Question_2_3_5">
    <title> Problem 5</title>
    <p>
        By the division algorithm, <m>a=3q</m>, <m>a=3q+1</m>, or <m>a=3q+2</m>. 
        <ul>
            <li>
                <p>
                    If <m>a=3q</m>, then <m>3|a</m>.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    If <m>a=3q+1</m>, then <m>a+2=3q+3=3(a+1)</m>, and <m>3|(a+2)</m>.
                </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <p>
                    If <m>a=3q+2</m>, then <m>a+4=3q+6=3(q+2)</m>, and <m>3|(a+4)</m>.
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </p>
</subsection>

